               <p>Q. Do you know the prisoner - A. Yes, he was employed by Mr. Sims in levelling the ground.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18090920-137-person1362">
                  PETER 
                  FARLEY
               <interp inst="t18090920-137-person1362" type="surname" value="FARLEY"></interp>
